Code Smells
===========

This tool is a cheat sheet for code smells.
All the information about codesmells comes from [source making](https://sourcemaking.com/refactoring/)

usage: codesmells
example usage: codesmells [category|codesmell|--argument]
	[category]:
		bloaters
		object-orientation-abusers
		change-preventers
		dispensables
		couplers
		other-smells
	[codesmell]:
		primitive-obsession
		long-method
		refused-bequest
	[--argument]:
		--help
		--update
